            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Press-Center/Press-releases/2008/strengthening-anti-discrimination-effort.html?id=531160" title="">
                        Strengthening anti-discrimination efforts
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 07.10.2008]</p>
                <p>The government has increased the resources of the Equality and Anti-Discrimination Ombud in 2009 by NOK 9 million in order to combat discrimination of people with disabilities and to strengthen existing anti-discrimination provisions. An additional NOK 4 million has been allocated for a new action plan against ethnic discrimination.</p>
                
                
